data.description: This lovely ground level condo is complete with 2 bedroom & 1 1/2 bathroom.  Nicely updated with fresh new carpet in the bedrooms, nice hardwood floors in the living room and in the hallway plus tile in the kitchen, dining area and the bathrooms.  This condo comes with 2 reserved parking spaces, plus additional guest parking.  There is a wood burning fireplace for the cool winter nights to come and AC for the hot summer days.  You can enjoy the warm summer/spring days sitting in the patio area or at the community pool.  All information deemed reliable but not guaranteed, Buyer and/or Buyer's agent must verify all information.
